# Install-required skills — installed on demand via `bash .claude/setup-skills.sh`.
# These are NEVER committed; each dev/session installs them locally.
# Bundled (committed) skills are the four re-included below.
.claude/skills/*
!.claude/skills/caveman/
!.claude/skills/ponytail/
!.claude/skills/superpowers/
!.claude/skills/ui-ux/

# ui-ux-pro-max-cli / skills-CLI / impeccable installers can also drop these:
# ui-ux-pro-max/, banner-design/, brand/, design/, design-system/, slides/,
# ui-styling/, design-taste-frontend/, minimalist-ui/, impeccable/ — all covered
# by the wildcard above.

# Lockfile written by the `skills` CLI on install — an install artifact, not tracked.
/skills-lock.json
